SystemInformationOperatingSystem.description:
This model encapsulates various pieces of
system-related information using Python's platform module. It provides a
structured way to access details about the system's hardware, operating
system, and interpreter version information.

hostname.description: The network name of the computer, possibly not fully qualified.
hostname.title: Hostname

operating_system.description: A detailed string identifying the underlying platform with as much useful information as possible.
operating_system.title: Platform

release.description: The system's release version, such as a version number or a name.
release.title: Release

system.description: The name of the operating system.
system.title: System

version.description: The specific release version of the system.
version.title: Version
